---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Services · AroraMSP"
  description="Microsoft 365 services: tenant audits, migrations, Entra ID, Intune deployment, and PowerShell automation. Four focused offers, enterprise depth, no reselling."
  page="services"
  canonical="https://aroramsp.com/services"
  ogTitle="Services - AroraMSP"
  ogDescription="Microsoft 365 services: tenant audits, migrations, Entra ID, Intune deployment, and PowerShell automation. Four focused offers, enterprise depth, no reselling."
>
  <section class="page wrap">
    <div class="page-head">
      <div class="sec-label">01 · services</div>
      <h2>Everything Microsoft 365, handled.</h2>
      <p>Four focused offers. Enterprise depth, no reselling, no middleman markups on licenses.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="services">
      <div class="service reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="n"><span>01</span><span class="tag">migration</span></div>
        <h3>M365 Migrations</h3>
        <p>Zero-downtime moves from Google Workspace, on-prem Exchange, or other tenants. Mail, files, Teams, identities.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cutover, staged, and hybrid</li>
          <li>Mailbox, OneDrive, SharePoint</li>
          <li>Cross-tenant and domain moves</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="n"><span>02</span><span class="tag">setup</span></div>
        <h3>Tenant Setup &amp; Config</h3>
        <p>Clean build from day one. Identity, Exchange, Teams, SharePoint, and DNS configured to best practice, not defaults.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Entra ID + Conditional Access</li>
          <li>SPF / DKIM / DMARC / MTA-STS</li>
          <li>Baseline policies + Intune</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="n"><span>03</span><span class="tag">security</span></div>
        <h3>Security Hardening</h3>
        <p>Defender, Purview, and Intune configured properly. Close the gaps your previous IT left open.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>MFA and passwordless rollout</li>
          <li>DLP and sensitivity labels</li>
          <li>Endpoint and mobile compliance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="service reveal reveal-delay-4">
        <div class="n"><span>04</span><span class="tag">optimize</span></div>
        <h3>Licensing Audit</h3>
        <p>Most SMBs overpay 20 to 40% on M365. I find unused licenses, wrong tiers, and redundant add-ons, then fix them.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Line-by-line license map</li>
          <li>Right-size E3 / E5 / Business</li>
          <li>Co-term and renewal strategy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
